These are Puzzles for 1x2 Level 4

.:: Puzzle 1x2-Level-4-1::.
The people prefer 2 different types of sport: parkour, skateboarding
1. the person who's sport is parkour is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |   2    |
| Sport   | skateboarding | parkour |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x2-Level-4-2::.
2 different games are played: domino, scrabble
1. the person playing scrabble is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1    |    2     |
| Game   | domino | scrabble |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x2-Level-4-3::.
